{"id": 2951, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得在社交网络上啥样的关系才算铁？", "description": "肯定不是“点赞之交”。（图片来源：istock ©️ roberuto）", "record_count": 2957, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190516164904Yk4TJLgZDqOnwojl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-22T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 344833, "content": "可以疯狂的表情刷\n用表情对话", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381695}, {"id": 344834, "content": "同一个窗口内同时进行多个话题的讨论。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501331}, {"id": 344836, "content": "可以突如其来的讲废话和琐碎的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617671}, {"id": 344838, "content": "一大长串的语音发过来，转化成文字，截图说普通话不标准的关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655216}, {"id": 344839, "content": "互喷脏话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1654590}, {"id": 344840, "content": "发消息必回~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655218}, {"id": 344841, "content": "有件事想跟她讲 知道她一定会回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038363}, {"id": 344845, "content": "可以借钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329728}, {"id": 344846, "content": "可以十多条消息在不同时间发给他，也不觉得尴尬", "image": "img/option/option/20190522142924AUlZb81svoDCtScy", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655241}, {"id": 344847, "content": "随时都能给他发消息并且不在意他回不回 互相随便吐槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052680}, {"id": 344848, "content": "可以互喷关系不变", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1589664}, {"id": 344849, "content": "能语音能视频", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300155}, {"id": 344853, "content": "无论何时，不论多久，不论多晚。那个人一直在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650326}, {"id": 344855, "content": "实时分享，无须刻意结束聊天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655282}, {"id": 344856, "content": "不用思考怎么结束聊天，自如的结束自如的开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655289}, {"id": 344857, "content": "想起什么话题就直接打，不用任何铺垫", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152781}, {"id": 345881, "content": "用一切办法催回消息，打电话发语音穷尽所能", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658051}, {"id": 344862, "content": "消息置顶🔝", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591683}, {"id": 344863, "content": "不用刻意说谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339725}, {"id": 344866, "content": "看到有趣的东西第一时间分享给她共享快乐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617248}, {"id": 344867, "content": "我可以随心所欲的发特定的表情，比如挖鼻屎...", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609303}, {"id": 344870, "content": "经常语音回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571386}, {"id": 344871, "content": "想聊天的时候可以随时发消息，可以是留言回复，可以是即时聊天～想结束聊天的时候也不用特意说再见～\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655347}, {"id": 345897, "content": "不用说什么，现实中见面就发自内心的那种微笑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658326}, {"id": 344874, "content": "不刻意地挑某个时间点一起聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655366}, {"id": 344107, "content": "按错一个表情也不需要撤回", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 344108, "content": "可以打视频call", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 344876, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/201905222126527PEkRj4hz0vrS1Ia.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1589464}, {"id": 344109, "content": "对方还没回复也可以继续给他发消息聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 689, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 344877, "content": "不回消息第二天见面也不会尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056087}, {"id": 344110, "content": "隔个两三天回复依然可以捡起上次没聊完的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 356, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 344878, "content": "遇到难题第一时间可以在线上的各种app找到对方，并且远程协助！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467857}, {"id": 344112, "content": "可以“鸡同鸭讲”地同时在说不同的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 231, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 344880, "content": "能把哪些在别人面前讲的会感觉到虚伪的话，到和ta聊就觉得真实无比，浪漫主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1650847}, {"id": 344894, "content": "能够分享今天遇到的事情！能够随时随地展开话题。不会着急等待，但开始对话就能聊很久！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1654334}, {"id": 344895, "content": "如何区分是真铁还是“长辈们”在网络社交中不分场合的尬聊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057388}, {"id": 344898, "content": "交流的关系较为稳定，即偶尔因忙碌无法聊天或只能隔三差五聊了一句，过了一个月闲下来了可以继续和之前一样聊天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498298}, {"id": 344900, "content": "互删以后还能互加，耸耸肩～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526096}, {"id": 344901, "content": "要帮忙有问题秒回", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361352}, {"id": 344902, "content": "各种对方才懂的黑话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361352}, {"id": 344903, "content": "没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533825}, {"id": 344904, "content": "有什么好笑的梗第一时间就想着要分享给对方，觉得对方能明白你的笑点或者槽点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127376}, {"id": 345160, "content": "打游戏互相觉得对方很坑,还一起玩", "image": "img/option/option/20190524133340gJPNFuBav4plzdGM.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574767}, {"id": 344906, "content": "可以无限吐槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611935}, {"id": 344907, "content": "不用花心思在对如何开始对话和如何结束对话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646207}, {"id": 344908, "content": "有属于仅限于两个人之间的 梗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927839}, {"id": 344910, "content": "不用时刻聊天，但是见了面依旧感情很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503046}, {"id": 344920, "content": "随时都能聊任何话题不用铺垫，随时可以不回复也无需解释！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655549}, {"id": 347484, "content": "可以电话、视频～不用躲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664497}, {"id": 346214, "content": "不管怎么样，都可以发信息给对方而不必担心对方反感。早安晚安是日常，也可以聊聊其他话题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}]}